           <h3>ABOUT US</h3>

           Fastlane Hypermarket first emerged as a result of a takeover of ABC Holdings Limited, 
        a South African company consisting of 6 wholesale units,which include Groceries, Electricals, Farming, Furniture, 
           Motoring, Chemicals and Clothing. Through the 2 decades of our 
        history, our Group has built on this foundation and has grown into a large and diverse business, operating in a number of sectors predominantly in 
        the Fast Moving Consumer Goods (“FMCG”) sector within Botswana, Namibia, Lesotho, South Africa and most recently, Australia.
